---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Get Involved" description="Join the CRE Trails volunteer community. Learn about volunteer opportunities, trail maintenance days, and how to support our trails.">
  <section style="padding-top: var(--spacing-xl);">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Get Involved</h1>
      <p class="text-center" style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--color-text-light); max-width: 800px; margin: var(--spacing-md) auto var(--spacing-xl);">
        Help us maintain and improve our community trails. No experience necessary - just bring your enthusiasm!
      </p>

      <div class="hero" style="height: auto; padding: var(--spacing-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);">
        <div class="hero-content" style="padding: 0;">
          <h2 style="color: var(--color-white);">Why Volunteer?</h2>
          <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">Our trails are maintained entirely by volunteers from our community. Your help keeps the trails safe, accessible, and beautiful for everyone to enjoy.</p>
          <div class="grid grid-3" style="gap: var(--spacing-md);">
            <div style="text-align: center;">
              <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);">ğŸ¤</div>
              <strong>Build Community</strong>
              <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: var(--spacing-xs);">Meet neighbors and make friends</p>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
              <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);">ğŸ’ª</div>
              <strong>Get Exercise</strong>
              <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: var(--spacing-xs);">Outdoor work and fresh air</p>
            </div>
            <div style="text-align: center;">
              <div style="font-size: 2.5rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);">ğŸŒŸ</div>
              <strong>Make an Impact</strong>
              <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: var(--spacing-xs);">See the direct results of your work</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-2">
        <div>
          <h2>Volunteer Opportunities</h2>
          
          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
            <div class="card-icon">ğŸ”¨</div>
            <h3>Trail Maintenance Days</h3>
            <p>Join us for scheduled work days to clear brush, remove debris, repair trail surfaces, and maintain signage.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);"><strong>Time Commitment:</strong> 2-4 hours per session</p>
            <p><strong>Frequency:</strong> Several times per year</p>
            <p><strong>What to Bring:</strong> Work gloves, water, appropriate clothing</p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-sm); font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-text-light);">
              Tools and equipment provided by the committee.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="card" style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">
            <div class="card-icon">ğŸ“‹</div>
            <h3>Trail Committee Member</h3>
            <p>Join the POACRE Trails Committee to help plan maintenance activities, coordinate volunteers, and make decisions about trail improvements.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);"><strong>Time Commitment:</strong> Quarterly meetings + occasional planning</p>
            <p><strong>Skills Needed:</strong> Organization, communication, passion for trails</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">ğŸ—ºï¸</div>
            <h3>Trail Monitoring</h3>
            <p>Help us keep tabs on trail conditions by reporting issues like fallen trees, erosion, damaged markers, or safety concerns.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);"><strong>Time Commitment:</strong> Ongoing, as you use the trails</p>
            <p><strong>How to Help:</strong> Simply contact us when you notice issues</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div class="card" style="background-color: var(--color-sage); color: var(--color-white);">
            <h2 style="color: var(--color-white);">Ready to Help?</h2>
            <p>We'd love to have you join our volunteer team! Here's how to get started:</p>
            
            <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: var(--spacing-md); border-radius: var(--border-radius);">
              <h3 style="color: var(--color-white); font-size: 1.125rem;">Contact Us</h3>
              <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);">
                <strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:443-975-4736" style="color: var(--color-white);">(443) 975-4736</a><br>
                <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:lydia@hotmail.com" style="color: var(--color-white);">lydia@hotmail.com</a>
              </p>
              <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">
                <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Send Us a Message</a>
              </p>
            </div>

            <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md); background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1); padding: var(--spacing-md); border-radius: var(--border-radius);">
              <h3 style="color: var(--color-white); font-size: 1.125rem;">Follow on Facebook</h3>
              <p>Stay updated on volunteer days and events:</p>
              <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);">
                <a href="https://www.facebook.com/CRE.Trails" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary">
                  <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" style="vertical-align: middle; margin-right: 8px;">
                    <path d="M24 12.073c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12s-12 5.373-12 12c0 5.99 4.388 10.954 10.125 11.854v-8.385H7.078v-3.47h3.047V9.43c0-3.007 1.792-4.669 4.533-4.669 1.312 0 2.686.235 2.686.235v2.953H15.83c-1.491 0-1.956.925-1.956 1.874v2.25h3.328l-.532 3.47h-2.796v8.385C19.612 23.027 24 18.062 24 12.073z"/>
                  </svg>
                  Follow Us
                </a>
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="info-box" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">
            <h3>â“ Frequently Asked Questions</h3>
            
            <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">
              <p><strong>Do I need experience?</strong></p>
              <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);">No! We welcome volunteers of all skill levels. We'll show you what to do.</p>

              <p><strong>What should I wear?</strong></p>
              <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);">Long pants, closed-toe shoes, and clothes you don't mind getting dirty. Bring work gloves if you have them.</p>

              <p><strong>Can I bring my family?</strong></p>
              <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);">Absolutely! Trail maintenance is a great family activity. Children should be supervised.</p>

              <p><strong>What if I can't commit to regular volunteering?</strong></p>
              <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);">That's fine! Come when you can. Even one work day makes a difference.</p>

              <p><strong>Are there age restrictions?</strong></p>
              <p>All ages welcome! Minors should be accompanied by an adult.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);">
        <h2>What Volunteers Do</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">Here are some of the activities our volunteers help with:</p>

        <div class="grid grid-3">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>ğŸŒ¿ Trail Clearing</h3>
            <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); line-height: 2;">
              <li>Remove fallen branches</li>
              <li>Clear overgrown vegetation</li>
              <li>Trim back encroaching brush</li>
              <li>Rake leaves from trail surface</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>ğŸ› ï¸ Trail Maintenance</h3>
            <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); line-height: 2;">
              <li>Fill in erosion areas</li>
              <li>Repair trail surfaces</li>
              <li>Install or repair drainage</li>
              <li>Build or maintain benches</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>ğŸª§ Signage & Marking</h3>
            <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); line-height: 2;">
              <li>Install trail markers</li>
              <li>Replace damaged signs</li>
              <li>Paint or refresh markers</li>
              <li>Update trail maps</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div style="margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);">
        <h2>Other Ways to Support</h2>
        <p style="margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">Can't volunteer your time? Here are other ways to support the trails:</p>

        <div class="grid grid-2">
          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">ğŸ’°</div>
            <h3>Donations</h3>
            <p>Financial contributions help purchase tools, materials, and supplies for trail maintenance.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);">Contact the committee to learn about donation options.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">ğŸ”§</div>
            <h3>Equipment & Supplies</h3>
            <p>Donate or lend tools and equipment for trail work days:</p>
            <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); margin-top: var(--spacing-sm); line-height: 1.8;">
              <li>Hand tools (rakes, shovels, pruners)</li>
              <li>Work gloves</li>
              <li>Wheelbarrows</li>
              <li>Safety equipment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">ğŸ“£</div>
            <h3>Spread the Word</h3>
            <p>Help us recruit more volunteers by:</p>
            <ul style="margin-left: var(--spacing-lg); margin-top: var(--spacing-sm); line-height: 1.8;">
              <li>Sharing our Facebook posts</li>
              <li>Telling neighbors about the trails</li>
              <li>Inviting friends to work days</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <div class="card-icon">ğŸ“¸</div>
            <h3>Document Our Work</h3>
            <p>Take photos during work days and events to share on social media and this website.</p>
            <p style="margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);">Help us showcase the great work our volunteers do!</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero" style="height: auto; padding: var(--spacing-xl); margin-top: var(--spacing-2xl);">
        <div class="hero-content" style="padding: 0; text-align: center;">
          <h2 style="color: var(--color-white); margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);">Join Our Trail Community Today!</h2>
          <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);">
            Every volunteer makes a difference. Whether you can give a few hours a year or want to be more involved, we'd love to have you on our team.
          </p>
          <div class="btn-group">
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us to Volunteer</a>
            <a href="https://www.facebook.com/CRE.Trails" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn btn-secondary">Follow on Facebook</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
